---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title="Experiencias Exclusivas | Casa L&G">
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="relative min-h-screen bg-luxury-dark text-white pt-32 overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-6">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/80 via-brand-dark/50 to-luxury-dark z-10"></div>
      <div class="w-full h-full bg-[#1a1111] opacity-40 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-20 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center">
      <p class="font-sans text-brand-gold tracking-[0.5em] text-[9px] md:text-[11px] uppercase mb-4 animate-fade-in">
        Momentos de Alta Gama
      </p>
      
      <h1 class="font-premium text-4xl md:text-7xl text-white mb-8 tracking-wide uppercase leading-tight">
        Experiencias <br/><span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-brand-gold to-white">Multisensoriales</span>
      </h1>
      
      <div class="h-[1px] w-16 bg-brand-gold/40 mb-8"></div>
      
      <p class="font-body text-white/70 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed tracking-wide mb-12 max-w-xl">
        Diseñamos eventos privados, catas exclusivas y talleres de personalización donde el lujo se siente a través de cada uno de los sentidos. Un espacio reservado para quienes aprecian el verdadero arte del detalle.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center">
        <a href="https://wa.me/51953435738" class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 border border-brand-gold overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-brand-gold">
          <span class="relative z-10 font-sans text-[10px] tracking-widest text-brand-gold group-hover:text-black uppercase transition-colors">
            Reservar Experiencia VIP
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .font-premium { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; }
</style>